OL,3,CMum pleads guilty to causing death of
OL,4,Cson, nine, by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA mother from Wiltshire has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to causing the death of her
OL,8,Fnine-year-old son by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FBarbara Roe, from Ludgershall,
OL,11,Fappeared at Bournemouth Crown Court on
OL,12,F6 March 2025, where she admitted the
OL,13,Fcharge.
OL,15,FHer son, Zac Roe, from Andover in
OL,16,FHampshire, died at the scene of the
OL,17,Fcrash in East Woodyates, north Dorset,
OL,18,Fon 25 March 2024.
