OL,6,FDorset Police was called to the
OL,7,Faccident on the A354 Salisbury Road
OL,8,Finvolving a cattle transporter truck
OL,9,Fand trailer, a white Ford Transit van
OL,10,Fand a grey Citroen car.
OL,12,FAt the plea hearing today, Thursday 6
OL,13,FMarch, the judge imposed an interim
OL,14,Fdriving ban on Barbara Roe until the
OL,15,Fsentencing hearing.
