OL,6,FReleasing the 39-year-old on
OL,7,Fconditional bail, Judge William
OL,8,FMousley KC told her: "You will be
OL,9,Fsentenced on Friday 2 May, if you do
OL,10,Fnot come to court on 2 May without a
OL,11,Fgood reason you will be committing a
OL,12,Fseparate offence for which you could
OL,13,Fbe separately punished.
OL,15,F"Were you to break the conditions of
OL,16,Fbail you could be arrested and
OL,17,Fremanded in custody.
