OL,6,FIn a statement, his father Josh Roe
OL,7,Fsaid: "Words cannot describe the pain
OL,8,FI'm feeling, my heart is broken. You
OL,9,Fare my little angel. I love you more
OL,10,Fthan anything in this world, you are
OL,11,Fmy best buddy."
OL,13,FGrandfather Chris Roe said: "Zac,
OL,14,Fthere are just no words to find. I
OL,15,Fjust want to thank you for the
OL,16,Fwonderful and fun-filled memories we
OL,17,Fshared on your short journey of your
OL,18,Flife.
